該都好欣慰<br />\n<br />\n但都搵個時候適當咁釋放情緒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649801a42be2adbe82a7e575e64569122200e0f0","tid":140324,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去海旁啤一啤佢 大聲啲講出黎 訓一教 第二日醒番又係一個新開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD大問題想忘記都唔係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過岩岩約左個fd放工去搵佢<br />\n好在都仲有傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef1cdaea10135f1dbf52b13ca3d968a17aab88d","tid":140324,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家😢😢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你都唔開心？<br />\n搵個朋友去下街散下心先啦<br />\n咩都唔做好易變抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6716b06b2a44c8a3249ac65e2a3718278860a930","tid":140324,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他知道 哭 是沒有用的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無睇inside out?<br />\n推薦大家去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf77cad19fd97f9d2407fe61f8a08774e15f5e59","tid":140324,"uid":88521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去海旁啤一啤佢 大聲啲講出黎 訓一教 第二日醒番又係一個新開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD大問題想忘記都唔係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過岩岩約左個fd放工去搵佢<br />\n好在都仲有傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你經歷得越多 除左屋企人同你重視既人會令你唔開心之外 其他野你都會當係浮雲 不過都同你講聲加油 無野係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如無傾訴對象咪揾我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67616e520c2118fccc177faa01f57e20194b525","tid":140324,"uid":50645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"確診cancer 果時，屋企人係格離，為左唔比佢地擔心，死忍唔喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ec565812608e2c8c8ab8e12c6dc4cb1b843ab7","tid":140324,"uid":87386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家😢😢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你都唔開心？<br />\n搵個朋友去下街散下心先啦<br />\n咩都唔做好易變抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番屋企喊一場冇事😶😶"},{"pid":"2a155654ee79999d1baa8142842bf11ae2563742","tid":140324,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去海旁啤一啤佢 大聲啲講出黎 訓一教 第二日醒番又係一個新開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD大問題想忘記都唔係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過岩岩約左個fd放工去搵佢<br />\n好在都仲有傾訴對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你經歷得越多 除左屋企人同你重視既人會令你唔開心之外 其他野你都會當係浮雲 不過都同你講聲加油 無野係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如無傾訴對象咪揾我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次就係屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我諗解決到既，但要俾d時間我放下負能量先<br />\n如果唔係唔夠勇力去面對問題<br />\n<br />\n巴打你好似經歷過好多好蒼桑咁既？"},{"pid":"45c9682f3761eb82171700c079a79fd3a1e28a2b","tid":140324,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"喪禮果陣 全程都忍緊 到要禁制嗰下差啲忍唔住喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩最後都無喊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3535c2d0ef2e5390878ab1129a6fa4a7ed88e74c","tid":140324,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:18:35.000Z","msg":"工作辛苦既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dad5fe869e2c2e6ffe6fac55acf5901e808c26","tid":140324,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>確診cancer 果時，屋企人係格離，為左唔比佢地擔心，死忍唔喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你真堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生死有命，但cancer又唔一定醫唔好既<br />\n心態好重要，積極面對都無咩唔好<br />\n多d陪下屋企人制造下d難忘回憶先啦<br />\n再整返個bucket list 做d挑戰自己既事<br />\n唔好令自己既人生留低悔恨<br />\n就算有，都起碼搵到d值得驕傲既事cover哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}